[OIE's WAHID follow-up report No. 1, dated 18 Apr 2014, is available at http://www.oie.int/wahis_2/public/wahid.php/Reviewreport/Review?page_refer=MapFullEventReport&reportid=15127.

Genotyping results to confirm (or otherwise) the similarity between the South Korean and Japanese strains, are anticipated. In South Korea, 26 HPAI H5N8 outbreaks have been reported between 16 Jan and 23 Feb 2014. Links to the 5 reports and an interactive map showing all outbreaks in this thread are available at http://www.oie.int/wahis_2/public/wahid.php/Reviewreport/Review/viewsummary?fupser=&dothis=&reportid=14668. - Mod.AS

